{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm the weekly tech critic for the New York Times."},{"time":2000,"text":"I review gadgets and stuff."},{"time":4000,"text":"And mostly what good dads should be doing this time of year"},{"time":8000,"text":"is nestling with their kids and decorating the Christmas tree."},{"time":11000,"text":"What I'm mostly doing this year"},{"time":13000,"text":"is going on cable TV and answering the same question:"},{"time":16000,"text":"\"What are the tech trends for next year?\""},{"time":19000,"text":"And I'm like, \"Didn't we just go through this last year?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":22000,"text":"But I'm going to pick the one that interests me most, and that is the"},{"time":25000,"text":"completed marriage of the cell phone and the Internet."},{"time":28000,"text":"You know, I found that volcano on Google Images,"},{"time":32000,"text":"not realizing how much it makes me look like the cover of Dianetics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38000,"text":"Anyway, this all started a few years ago,"},{"time":40000,"text":"when they started carrying your voice over the Internet rather than over a phone line,"},{"time":45000,"text":"and we've come a long way since that."},{"time":47000,"text":"But that was interesting in itself. This is companies like Vonage."},{"time":50000,"text":"Basically you take an ordinary telephone, you plug it into this little box"},{"time":52000,"text":"that they give you and the box plugs into your cable modem."},{"time":55000,"text":"Now, it works just like a regular phone."},{"time":57000,"text":"So you can pick up the phone, you hear a dial tone,"},{"time":59000,"text":"but its just a fake-out. It's a WAV file of a dial tone,"},{"time":64000,"text":"just to reassure you that the world hasn't ended."},{"time":67000,"text":"It could be anything. It could be salsa music"},{"time":69000,"text":"or a comedy routine -- it doesn't matter."},{"time":72000,"text":"The little box has your phone number."},{"time":74000,"text":"So that's really cool -- you can take it to London or Siberia,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and your next door neighbor can dial your home number and your phone will ring,"},{"time":81000,"text":"because it's got everything in the box."},{"time":83000,"text":"They've got every feature known to man in there,"},{"time":85000,"text":"because adding a new feature is just software."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"And as a result of Voice Over IP --"},{"time":91000,"text":"I hate that term -- Voice Over Internet --"},{"time":93000,"text":"land-line home-phone service has gone down 30 percent in the last three years."},{"time":98000,"text":"I mean, no self-respecting college kid has home phone service anymore."},{"time":103000,"text":"This is what college kids are more likely to have. It's the most popular"},{"time":105000,"text":"VOIP service in the world: It's Skype."},{"time":107000,"text":"It's a free program you download for your Mac or PC,"},{"time":109000,"text":"and you make free phone calls anywhere in the world"},{"time":112000,"text":"The downside is that you have to wear a headset like a nerd."},{"time":115000,"text":"It's not your phone -- it's your computer."},{"time":119000,"text":"But nonetheless, if you're a college kid and you have no money,"},{"time":121000,"text":"believe me, this is better than trying to use your cell phone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124000,"text":"It's really cute seeing middle-aged people"},{"time":127000,"text":"like me, try out Skype for the first time,"},{"time":129000,"text":"which is usually when their kid goes away for a semester abroad."},{"time":132000,"text":"They don't want to pay the international fees,"},{"time":134000,"text":"so they're like, \"Timmy! Is that you?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":139000,"text":"It's really cute."},{"time":142000,"text":"But I -- at least it was when I did it --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"I think where VOIP is really going to get interesting"},{"time":147000,"text":"is when they start putting it on cell phones."},{"time":149000,"text":"Imagine if you had an ordinary cell phone,"},{"time":151000,"text":"and any time you were in a wireless hotspot --"},{"time":153000,"text":"free calls anywhere in the world,"},{"time":156000,"text":"never pay the cellular company a nickel."},{"time":159000,"text":"It'd be really, really cool -- and yet,"},{"time":161000,"text":"even though the technology for this has been available"},{"time":163000,"text":"for five years, incredibly,"},{"time":166000,"text":"the number of standard cell phones"},{"time":168000,"text":"offered by US carriers with free VOIP"},{"time":171000,"text":"is zero!"},{"time":174000,"text":"I can't figure out why!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178000,"text":"Actually, I need to update that. There's one now."},{"time":181000,"text":"And it's so interesting that I thought I would tell you about it."},{"time":184000,"text":"It comes from T-Mobile."},{"time":186000,"text":"And I am not paid by T-Mobile."},{"time":188000,"text":"I'm not plugging T-Mobile."},{"time":190000,"text":"The New York Times has very rigid policies about that."},{"time":193000,"text":"Ever since that Jayson Blair jerk ruined it for all of us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":198000,"text":"Basically, the reason you haven't heard about this program"},{"time":200000,"text":"is because it was introduced last year"},{"time":202000,"text":"on June 29."},{"time":204000,"text":"Does anyone remember what else happened on June 29 last year?"},{"time":208000,"text":"It was the iPhone. The iPhone came out that day."},{"time":210000,"text":"I'm like, can you imagine being the"},{"time":212000,"text":"T-Mobile PR lady? You know?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"\"Hi, we have an announcement to -- WAH!!!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"But it's actually really, really cool. You have a choice of phones,"},{"time":228000,"text":"and we're not talking smartphones --"},{"time":230000,"text":"ordinary phones, including a Blackberry, that have Wi-Fi."},{"time":233000,"text":"The deal is, any time you're in a Wi-Fi hotspot,"},{"time":236000,"text":"all your calls are free."},{"time":238000,"text":"And when you're out of the hotspot, you're on the regular cellular network."},{"time":241000,"text":"You're thinking, \"Well, how often am I in a hotspot?\""},{"time":243000,"text":"The answer is, \"All the time!\""},{"time":245000,"text":"Because they give you"},{"time":247000,"text":"a regular wireless router that works with the phone,"},{"time":249000,"text":"for your house."},{"time":251000,"text":"Which is really ingenious, because we all know that"},{"time":253000,"text":"T-Mobile is the most pathetic carrier."},{"time":255000,"text":"They have coverage like the size of my thumbnail."},{"time":258000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":260000,"text":"But it's a hundred million dollars to put up one of those towers. Right?"},{"time":263000,"text":"They don't have that kind of money. Instead they give each of us"},{"time":266000,"text":"a seven-dollar-and-95-cent box. They're like a stealth tower installation program."},{"time":271000,"text":"We're putting it in our homes for them!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275000,"text":"Anyway, they have Wi-Fi phones in Europe."},{"time":278000,"text":"But the thing that T-Mobile did that nobody's done before"},{"time":280000,"text":"is, when you're on a call an you move from Wi-Fi into cellular range,"},{"time":284000,"text":"the call is handed off in mid-syllable,"},{"time":287000,"text":"seamlessly. I'll show you the advanced technologies"},{"time":291000,"text":"we use at the New York Times to test this gear."},{"time":294000,"text":"This is me with a camcorder on a phone"},{"time":296000,"text":"going like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"As I walk out of the house from my Wi-Fi hotspot"},{"time":301000,"text":"into the cellular network on a call with my wife --"},{"time":304000,"text":"look at the upper left. That's the Wi-Fi signal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307000,"text":"(Video): Jennifer Pogue: Hello?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"David Pogue: Hi babes, it's me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"JP: Oh, hi darling, how are you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313000,"text":"DP: You're on Wi-Fi. How does it sound?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":315000,"text":"JP: Oh, it sounds pretty good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":317000,"text":"Now, I'm leaving the house. DP: I'm going for a walk -- do you mind?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"JP: No not at all. I'm having a great day with the kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"DP: What are you guys doing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":325000,"text":"Right there!"},{"time":327000,"text":"It just changed to the cellular tower in mid-call."},{"time":330000,"text":"I don't know why my wife says I never listen to her. I don't get that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":333000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"The bottom line is that the boundaries,"},{"time":339000,"text":"because of the Internet plus cell phone, are melting."},{"time":341000,"text":"The cool thing about the T-Mobile phones"},{"time":343000,"text":"is that although switching technologies is very advanced,"},{"time":346000,"text":"the billing technology has not caught up."},{"time":350000,"text":"So what I mean is that you can start a call"},{"time":352000,"text":"in your house in the Wi-Fi hotspot,"},{"time":355000,"text":"you can get in your car and talk until the battery's dead --"},{"time":358000,"text":"which would be like 10 minutes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":361000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":362000,"text":"And the call will continue to be free."},{"time":364000,"text":"Because they don't, they haven't --"},{"time":366000,"text":"well, no, wait! Not so fast."},{"time":368000,"text":"It also works the other way."},{"time":370000,"text":"So if you start a call on your cellular network"},{"time":372000,"text":"and you come home, you keep being billed."},{"time":374000,"text":"Which is why most people with this service"},{"time":376000,"text":"get into the habit of saying,"},{"time":378000,"text":"\"Hey, I just got home. Can I call you right back?\""},{"time":380000,"text":"Now you get it."},{"time":382000,"text":"It's also true that if you use one of these phones overseas,"},{"time":385000,"text":"it doesn't know what Internet hotspot you're in."},{"time":388000,"text":"On the Internet nobody knows you're a dog,"},{"time":390000,"text":"right? Nobody knows you're in Pakistan."},{"time":393000,"text":"You can make free unlimited calls"},{"time":395000,"text":"home to the US with these phones. So, very, very interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":398000,"text":"This is another favorite of mine."},{"time":400000,"text":"Does anyone here have a working cell phone"},{"time":403000,"text":"that's on, with coverage, who can make a call right now without a lot of fussing?"},{"time":407000,"text":"OK. Would you call me please right now? [Phone number given.]"},{"time":414000,"text":"And don't you all call me at three a.m. asking me to fix your printer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":418000,"text":"I have two cell phones, so this going to be very odd, if it works."},{"time":421000,"text":"I should know not to do technology demos"},{"time":423000,"text":"in front of an audience. It's just, like, absurd."},{"time":429000,"text":"This one is going off. And -- oh, I have the ringer off. Tsh! Great."},{"time":435000,"text":"Anyway, this one is also going off. So they're both ringing at the same time."},{"time":438000,"text":"Excuse me one second."},{"time":440000,"text":"Hello?"},{"time":442000,"text":"Oh. Where are you calling from?"},{"time":444000,"text":"No, no just kidding. There he is. Thank you very much for doing that."},{"time":446000,"text":"I didn't even know it was you -- I was looking at this guy."},{"time":449000,"text":"Oh great! Yeah. Yeah you can all stop calling now!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":452000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":455000,"text":"All right! We've made the point."},{"time":459000,"text":"All right. Ringer off. Everyone wants in on the action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":464000,"text":"So this is Grand Central at work -- it's a --"},{"time":467000,"text":"oh, for gods sake!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"I have your numbers now!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":473000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":475000,"text":"You will pay."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477000,"text":"Grand Central is this really brilliant idea"},{"time":479000,"text":"where they give you a new phone number,"},{"time":482000,"text":"and then at that point one phone number rings all your phones at once."},{"time":486000,"text":"Your home phone, your work phone, your cell phone, your yacht phone"},{"time":489000,"text":"(this is the EG crowd)."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":493000,"text":"The beauty of that is you never miss a call."},{"time":495000,"text":"I know a lot of you are like,"},{"time":497000,"text":"\"Ooh, I don't want to be reached at any hour.\""},{"time":499000,"text":"But the beauty is it's all going through the internet,"},{"time":501000,"text":"so you get all of these really cool features --"},{"time":503000,"text":"like you can say, I want these people to be able to call me only during these hours."},{"time":507000,"text":"And I want these people to hear this greeting,"},{"time":510000,"text":"\"Hi boss, I'm out making us both some money. Leave a message.\""},{"time":513000,"text":"And then your wife calls, and, \"Hi honey, leave me a message.\""},{"time":516000,"text":"Very, very customizable."},{"time":519000,"text":"Google bought it, and they've been working on it for a year."},{"time":523000,"text":"They're supposed to come out with it very shortly in a public method."}]},{"cues":[{"time":526000,"text":"By the way, this is something that really bothers me."},{"time":529000,"text":"I don't know if you realize this. When you call 411 on your cell phone,"},{"time":533000,"text":"they charge you two bucks."},{"time":535000,"text":"Did you know that? It's an outrage."},{"time":537000,"text":"I actually got a photograph of the Verizon employee right there."},{"time":540000,"text":"I'm going to tell you how to avoid that now."},{"time":542000,"text":"What you're going to use is Google Cellular."},{"time":544000,"text":"It's totally free -- there's not even ads."},{"time":547000,"text":"If you know how to send a text message, you can get the same information for free."},{"time":549000,"text":"I'm about to change your life. So here's me doing it."},{"time":552000,"text":"You send a text message to the word \"Google,\""},{"time":555000,"text":"which turns out to be 46645."},{"time":557000,"text":"Leave off the last \"e\" for savings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560000,"text":"Anyway, so lets say you need a drugstore near Chicago."},{"time":562000,"text":"You type \"pharmacy Chicago,\" or the zip code."},{"time":564000,"text":"You hit send, and in five seconds,"},{"time":568000,"text":"they will send you back the two closest drugstores,"},{"time":572000,"text":"complete with name address and phone number."},{"time":574000,"text":"Here it comes."},{"time":576000,"text":"And it's already written down -- so, like, if you're driving,"},{"time":578000,"text":"you don't have to do one of these things, \"Uh huh, uh huh, uh huh.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":581000,"text":"It works with weather, too."},{"time":583000,"text":"You can say \"Weather,\" and the name of the city you're going to travel to."},{"time":585000,"text":"And then in five seconds, they send you back"},{"time":588000,"text":"the complete weather forecast for that town."},{"time":591000,"text":"Shortly I'll tell you why I was in Milan."},{"time":594000,"text":"Here we go. And those are just the beginning."},{"time":596000,"text":"These are all the different things that you can text to Google and they will --"},{"time":599000,"text":"yeah! You're all trying to write this down."},{"time":601000,"text":"That's cute. I do have an email address. You can just ask me."},{"time":606000,"text":"It's absolutely phenomenal. The only downside"},{"time":608000,"text":"is that it requires you to know how to text --"},{"time":610000,"text":"send a text message. Nobody over 40 knows how to do that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613000,"text":"So I'm going to teach you something even better."},{"time":615000,"text":"This is called Google Info."},{"time":617000,"text":"They've just launched this voice-activated version of the same thing."},{"time":619000,"text":"It's speech recognition like you've never heard before."},{"time":622000,"text":"So lets say I'm in Monterey,"},{"time":624000,"text":"and I want what?"},{"time":626000,"text":"I want to find what? Bagels. OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":629000,"text":"Google: Say the business and the city and state."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633000,"text":"DP: Bagels, Monterey, California."},{"time":639000,"text":"I got the Chinese line."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":643000,"text":"Google: Bagels, Monterey, California."},{"time":645000,"text":"Top eight results: Number one,"},{"time":647000,"text":"Bagel Bakery on El Dorado Street."},{"time":650000,"text":"To select number one, you can press one or say \"number one.\""},{"time":654000,"text":"Number two: Bagel Bakery, commissary department."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658000,"text":"Number Two. Number Two. Two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":669000,"text":"Why do I listen to people in the audience?"},{"time":672000,"text":"Well anyway -- oh! Here we go!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":674000,"text":"Google: ... commissary department on McClellan Avenue, Monterey."},{"time":677000,"text":"I'll connect you, or say \"details,\" or \"go back.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":680000,"text":"DP: He's connecting me! He doesn't even tell me the phone number."},{"time":682000,"text":"He's just connecting me directly. It's like having a personal valet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688000,"text":"Google: Hold on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":692000,"text":"DP: Hi, could I have 400 with a schmear?"},{"time":694000,"text":"No, no, no -- just kidding, no no."},{"time":697000,"text":"So anyway, you never even find out the number."},{"time":701000,"text":"It's just so amazing."},{"time":703000,"text":"And it has incredible, incredible accuracy."},{"time":705000,"text":"This is even more amazing. Put this in your speed dial."},{"time":707000,"text":"This you can ask by voice any question."},{"time":711000,"text":"Who won the 1958 World Series?"},{"time":713000,"text":"What's the recipe for a certain cocktail?"},{"time":715000,"text":"It's absolutely amazing -- and they text you back the answer."},{"time":718000,"text":"I tried this this morning just to make sure it's still alive."},{"time":720000,"text":"\"Which actors have played James Bond?\""},{"time":722000,"text":"They text me back this: \"Sean Connery,"},{"time":724000,"text":"George Lazenby, Roger Moore, Timothy Dalton, Pierce Brosnan, Daniel Craig.\""},{"time":727000,"text":"Right! And then I was trying to pretend I was like a Valley girl."},{"time":729000,"text":"I'm like, \"What's the word that means you know, like,"},{"time":731000,"text":"when the sun, the moon and the earth are, like, all in a line?\""},{"time":734000,"text":"Just to see how the recognition was."},{"time":736000,"text":"They texted me back, \"It's called a syzygy.\""},{"time":739000,"text":"Which I knew, because it's the word that won me the Ohio spelling bee in 1976."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743000,"text":"You know, there's a lot of people wondering, \"How on earth are they going to"},{"time":745000,"text":"make money doing this?\" And the answer is: look at the last line."},{"time":748000,"text":"They put this teeny-weeny little ad, about 10 characters long."},{"time":751000,"text":"And a lot of people also want to know, \"How does it work?"},{"time":753000,"text":"How can it be so good? It's as though there is a human being"},{"time":756000,"text":"on the other end of the line.\""},{"time":758000,"text":"Because there is one!"},{"time":760000,"text":"They have 10,000 people"},{"time":762000,"text":"who are being paid 20 cents per answer."},{"time":765000,"text":"As you can imagine, it's college kids and old people."},{"time":769000,"text":"That's who can afford to do that."},{"time":771000,"text":"But it's a human being on the line. And it's gotten me out of so many"},{"time":775000,"text":"tough positions like, \"When's the last flight out of Chicago?\""},{"time":778000,"text":"You know. It's just absolutely amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":780000,"text":"Another thing that really bothers me about cell phones today --"},{"time":783000,"text":"this is probably my biggest pet peeve in all of technology."},{"time":787000,"text":"When I call to leave you a message,"},{"time":791000,"text":"I get 15 seconds of instructions"},{"time":795000,"text":"from a third-grade teacher on Ambien!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":799000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":800000,"text":"\"To page this person ... \""},{"time":802000,"text":"Page? What is this, 1975?"},{"time":806000,"text":"Nobody has pagers anymore."},{"time":808000,"text":"\"You may begin speaking at the tone."},{"time":811000,"text":"When you have finished recording,"},{"time":814000,"text":"you may hang up.\" No!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":817000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":821000,"text":"And then it gets worse:"},{"time":823000,"text":"when I call to retrieve my messages,"},{"time":826000,"text":"first of all: \"You have 87 messages."},{"time":831000,"text":"To listen to your messages ... \""},{"time":833000,"text":"Why else am I calling?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":835000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":837000,"text":"Of course I want to listen to the messages!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":841000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":843000,"text":"Oh! You all have cell phones too."},{"time":846000,"text":"So last year I went to Milan, Italy,"},{"time":849000,"text":"and I got to speak to an audience"},{"time":851000,"text":"of cellular executives from 200 countries around the world."},{"time":855000,"text":"And I said as a joke -- as a joke, I said,"},{"time":858000,"text":"\"I did the math. Verizon has 70 million customers."},{"time":861000,"text":"If you check your voicemail twice a day,"},{"time":864000,"text":"that's 100 million dollars a year."},{"time":867000,"text":"I bet you guys are doing this just to run up our airtime, aren't you?\""},{"time":871000,"text":"No chuckle. They're like this --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":874000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":877000,"text":"Where is the outrage, people? Rise up!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":881000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":884000,"text":"Sorry. I'm not bitter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":887000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":893000,"text":"So now I'm going to tell you how to get out of that."},{"time":895000,"text":"There are these services that transcribe"},{"time":897000,"text":"your voicemail into text."},{"time":900000,"text":"And they send it either to your email"},{"time":902000,"text":"or as text messages to your phone."},{"time":905000,"text":"It is a life-changer."},{"time":907000,"text":"And by the way, they don't always get the words right,"},{"time":909000,"text":"because it's over the phone and all that."},{"time":910000,"text":"So they attach the audio file at the bottom of the email"},{"time":913000,"text":"so you can listen to double-check."},{"time":915000,"text":"The services are called things like Spinvox,"},{"time":917000,"text":"Phonetag -- this is the one I use --"},{"time":919000,"text":"Callwave. A lot of people say, \"How are they doing this?"},{"time":921000,"text":"I don't really want people listening in to my calls.\""},{"time":924000,"text":"The executives at these companies told me,"},{"time":926000,"text":"\"Well we use a proprietary B-to-B, best-of-breed, peer-to-peer soluti -- \" you know."},{"time":931000,"text":"I think basically it's like these guys in India with headsets, you know, listening in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":936000,"text":"The reason I think that is that"},{"time":938000,"text":"on the first day I tried one of these services,"},{"time":940000,"text":"I got two voicemail messages. One was from a guy named Michael Stevenson,"},{"time":943000,"text":"which shouldn't be that hard to transcribe, and it was misspelled."},{"time":946000,"text":"The other was from my video producer at the Times, whose name is Vijaiy Singh,"},{"time":951000,"text":"with the silent 'h'. Nailed that one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":954000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":960000,"text":"So you be the judge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":962000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":964000,"text":"Anyway, this service, Callwave, promises"},{"time":967000,"text":"that it's all software -- nobody is listening to your messages."},{"time":969000,"text":"And they also promise that they're going to transcribe only the gist"},{"time":973000,"text":"of your messages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":975000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":978000,"text":"So I thought I'd see how that goes."},{"time":980000,"text":"This is me testing it out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":983000,"text":"(Video): Hello, this is Michael."},{"time":985000,"text":"Hope you're doing well. I'm fine here. Everything's good."},{"time":989000,"text":"Hey, I was walking along the street and the sky was blue."},{"time":994000,"text":"And your daughter broke her leg at soccer practice."},{"time":1000000,"text":"I'm going to have a sandwich for lunch."},{"time":1003000,"text":"She's in room -- emergency room 53W."},{"time":1008000,"text":"OK, talk to you later -- bye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1011000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1016000,"text":"I love my job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1018000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1019000,"text":"So a couple minutes later, this I got by email."},{"time":1021000,"text":"It's a very good transcription. But a couple minutes after that,"},{"time":1024000,"text":"I got the text message version. Now remember,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"a text message can only be 160 characters long."},{"time":1028000,"text":"So it had better be the gist of the gist, right?"},{"time":1033000,"text":"I'm not kidding you. The message said,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1035000,"text":"\"Was walking along the street\" and \"sky was blue\" and \"emergency\"!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1040000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1044000,"text":"What the f -- ?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1046000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1049000,"text":"Well I guess that was the gist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1054000,"text":"And lastly, I just have to talk about this one."},{"time":1056000,"text":"This is my favorite of all time. It's called Popularitydialer.com."},{"time":1059000,"text":"Basically, you're going to go on some"},{"time":1062000,"text":"iffy date, or a potentially bad meeting."},{"time":1064000,"text":"So you go and you type in your phone number,"},{"time":1067000,"text":"and at the exact minute where you want to be called --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1070000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1072000,"text":"And at that moment your phone will ring."},{"time":1074000,"text":"And you're like, \"I'm sorry. I've got to take this.\""},{"time":1076000,"text":"The really beautiful thing is,"},{"time":1078000,"text":"you know how when somebody's sitting next to you, sometimes they can sort of"},{"time":1080000,"text":"hear a little bit of the caller."},{"time":1083000,"text":"So they give you a choice"},{"time":1086000,"text":"of what you want to hear on the other end."},{"time":1088000,"text":"Here's the girlfriend."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1090000,"text":"Phone: Hey you, what's going on?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1092000,"text":"DP: I'm kinda, like, giving a talk right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1094000,"text":"Phone: Well, that's good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1096000,"text":"DP: What are you doing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1097000,"text":"Phone: I was just wondering what you were up to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1099000,"text":"DP: Right, I can't really talk right now."},{"time":1102000,"text":"This is the -- I love this -- the boss call."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1104000,"text":"Phone: Hey, this is Mr. Johnson calling from the office."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1107000,"text":"DP: Oh, hi, sir."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1108000,"text":"Phone: Did you complete that thing about a month ago? That photocopier training?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1111000,"text":"DP: Oh -- sorry I forgot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1114000,"text":"Phone: Yeah, well so when was the last time you used the photocopier?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1118000,"text":"DP: It was like three weeks ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1120000,"text":"Phone: Well, I don't know if you heard, you might have heard from Lenny, but --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1124000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1128000,"text":"I think the biggest change when Internet met phone"},{"time":1130000,"text":"was with the iPhone."},{"time":1132000,"text":"Not my finest moment in New York Times journalism."},{"time":1134000,"text":"It was when in the fall of 2006,"},{"time":1136000,"text":"I explained why Apple would never do a cell phone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1140000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1141000,"text":"I looked like a moron. However, my logic was good,"},{"time":1144000,"text":"because -- I don't know if you realize this, but -- until the iPhone came along,"},{"time":1147000,"text":"the carriers -- Verizon, AT&amp;T, Cingular --"},{"time":1150000,"text":"held veto power over every aspect"},{"time":1152000,"text":"of every design of every phone."},{"time":1154000,"text":"I know the people who worked on the Treo."},{"time":1156000,"text":"They went around to these carriers and said,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1158000,"text":"\"Look at these cool features.\" And Verizon is like, \"Hmm, no."},{"time":1161000,"text":"I don't think so.\""},{"time":1163000,"text":"It was not very conducive to innovation."},{"time":1167000,"text":"What I didn't anticipate was that Steve Jobs"},{"time":1169000,"text":"went around and said, \"Tell you what -- I'll give you a five-year exclusive"},{"time":1173000,"text":"if you'll let me design this phone in peace --"},{"time":1175000,"text":"and you won't even see it till it's done.\""},{"time":1177000,"text":"Actually, even so, he was turned down by Verizon and others."},{"time":1180000,"text":"Finally Cingular said OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1183000,"text":"I'm going to talk about the effect of the iPhone."},{"time":1185000,"text":"Please don't corner me at the party tonight"},{"time":1187000,"text":"and go, \"What are you? An Apple fan boy?\""},{"time":1189000,"text":"- you know. I'm not."},{"time":1191000,"text":"You can see what I said about it. It's a flawed masterpiece."},{"time":1194000,"text":"It's got bad things and good things. Lets all acknowledge that right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1197000,"text":"But it did change a few things. The first thing it changed"},{"time":1200000,"text":"was that all those carriers saw"},{"time":1202000,"text":"that they sold 10 million of these things in a year."},{"time":1205000,"text":"And they said, \"Oh my gosh, maybe we've been doing it wrong."},{"time":1207000,"text":"Maybe we should let phone designers design the phones.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1211000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1215000,"text":"Another thing was that it let 10 million people,"},{"time":1218000,"text":"for the first time, experience being online all the time."},{"time":1221000,"text":"Not using these 60-dollar-a-month"},{"time":1223000,"text":"cellular cards for their laptops."},{"time":1226000,"text":"I don't understand why we're not there yet."},{"time":1228000,"text":"When I'm an old man, I'm going to tell my grandchildren,"},{"time":1231000,"text":"\"When I was your age, if I wanted to check my email,"},{"time":1233000,"text":"I used to drive around town looking for a coffee shop. I did!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1237000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1244000,"text":"\"We had wireless base stations that could"},{"time":1246000,"text":"broadcast -- yay, about 150 feet across.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1249000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1250000,"text":"It's absurd. We have power outlets"},{"time":1252000,"text":"in every room of every building. We have running water."},{"time":1254000,"text":"What's the problem?"},{"time":1256000,"text":"Anyway -- but this teaches people what it's like."},{"time":1259000,"text":"You have to go to YouTube"},{"time":1261000,"text":"and type in \"iPhone Shuffle.\""},{"time":1263000,"text":"This guy did a mock video of one"},{"time":1265000,"text":"that's one inch square, like the real iPod Shuffle."},{"time":1268000,"text":"It's like, \"It only has one button."},{"time":1271000,"text":"Touch it and it dials a number at random.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1274000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1275000,"text":"\"Who the hell is this?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1277000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1278000,"text":"But the other thing it did"},{"time":1280000,"text":"is it opened up this idea of an app store."},{"time":1282000,"text":"It downloads right to the phone."},{"time":1285000,"text":"And you can use the tilt sensor"},{"time":1288000,"text":"to steer this car using this game."},{"time":1290000,"text":"These programs can use all the components"},{"time":1293000,"text":"of the iPhone -- the touch screen."},{"time":1295000,"text":"This is the Etch-A-Sketch program -- the theme of EG 2008."},{"time":1297000,"text":"You know how you erase it?"},{"time":1299000,"text":"Of course. You shake it."},{"time":1301000,"text":"Right, of course. We shake it to erase, like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1304000,"text":"They have 10,000 of these programs."},{"time":1306000,"text":"This is the translator program. They have every language in the world."},{"time":1309000,"text":"You type in what you want, and it gives you the translation."},{"time":1313000,"text":"This is amazing. This is Midomi."},{"time":1317000,"text":"A song is running through your head --"},{"time":1319000,"text":"you sing it into the thing:"},{"time":1320000,"text":"do do do do do, da da da da da da, da dum ..."},{"time":1325000,"text":"OK, you tap, \"Done\" and it will find out the song and play it for you."},{"time":1336000,"text":"I know. It's insane, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1340000,"text":"This is Pandora. Free Internet radio. Not just free Internet radio --"},{"time":1343000,"text":"you type in a band or a song name."},{"time":1345000,"text":"It will immediately play you that song or that band."},{"time":1348000,"text":"It has a thumbs-up and a thumbs-down."},{"time":1350000,"text":"You say if you like this song or not."},{"time":1353000,"text":"If you like it, it tries another song on you"},{"time":1355000,"text":"from a different band, with the same instrumentation, vocals,"},{"time":1358000,"text":"theme and tempo."},{"time":1360000,"text":"If you like that one, or don't like it,"},{"time":1362000,"text":"you do thumbs-up and thumbs-down. Over time it tailors the songs"},{"time":1365000,"text":"so that it completely stops playing bad songs."},{"time":1369000,"text":"It eventually only plays songs you like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1371000,"text":"This is Urbanspoon. You're in a city. It knows from GPS where you're standing."},{"time":1375000,"text":"You want to find a place to eat. You shake it."},{"time":1377000,"text":"It proposes a restaurant."},{"time":1380000,"text":"It gives you the price, and the location and ratings."},{"time":1384000,"text":"Video: I'm not going all the way to Flushing."},{"time":1389000,"text":"Anyway, just amazing, amazing things."},{"time":1391000,"text":"Of course, its not just about the iPhone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1393000,"text":"The iPhone broke the dyke, the wall."},{"time":1395000,"text":"But now it's everybody else. So Google has done their own Android operating system"},{"time":1399000,"text":"that will soon be on handsets -- phones from 34 companies."},{"time":1402000,"text":"Touch screen -- very, very nice."},{"time":1404000,"text":"Also with its own app store, where you can download programs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1407000,"text":"This is amazing. In the wake of all this,"},{"time":1410000,"text":"Verizon, the most calcified, corporate,"},{"time":1413000,"text":"conservative carrier of all,"},{"time":1415000,"text":"said, \"You can use any phone you want on our network.\""},{"time":1418000,"text":"I love the Wired headline:"},{"time":1420000,"text":"Pigs Fly, Hell Freezes Over"},{"time":1422000,"text":"and Verizon Opens Up Its Network -- No. Really."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1425000,"text":"So everything is changing. We've entered"},{"time":1427000,"text":"a new world of innovation, where the cell phone becomes your laptop,"},{"time":1432000,"text":"customized the way you want it."},{"time":1434000,"text":"Every cell phone is unique. There is software that you can add on."},{"time":1437000,"text":"Can I do one more one-minute song? Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1441000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1444000,"text":"Just to round it up -- this is the new Apple Power Music Stand."},{"time":1448000,"text":"It's only three pounds,"},{"time":1450000,"text":"or 12 if you install Microsoft Office."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1453000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1455000,"text":"Sorry, that was mean."},{"time":1458000,"text":"This is a song I did for the New York Times website as a music video."},{"time":1461000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, for seven blissful hours"},{"time":1464000,"text":"it was the number one video on YouTube."},{"time":1467537,"text":"(To the tune of \"My Way\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1468883,"text":"And now the end is near."},{"time":1473000,"text":"I'm sick to death"},{"time":1475000,"text":"of this old cell phone."},{"time":1478000,"text":"Bad sound, the signal's weak,"},{"time":1481000,"text":"the software stinks."},{"time":1483000,"text":"A made-in-Hell phone."},{"time":1486000,"text":"I've heard there's something new --"},{"time":1490000,"text":"a million times more rad than my phone."},{"time":1494000,"text":"I too will join the cult."},{"time":1498000,"text":"I want an iPhone."},{"time":1503000,"text":"Concerns -- I have a few. It's got some flaws;"},{"time":1508000,"text":"we may just face it."},{"time":1511000,"text":"No keys, no memory card,"},{"time":1514000,"text":"the battery's sealed --"},{"time":1516000,"text":"you can't replace it."},{"time":1519000,"text":"But God, this thing is sweet."},{"time":1522000,"text":"A multitouch, iPod, Wi-Fi phone."},{"time":1527000,"text":"You had me from, \"Hello.\""},{"time":1531000,"text":"I want an iPhone."},{"time":1535000,"text":"I want to touch its precious screen."},{"time":1539000,"text":"I want to wipe the smudges clean."},{"time":1543000,"text":"I want my friends to look and drool."},{"time":1547000,"text":"I want to say, \"Look -- now I'm cool\""},{"time":1551000,"text":"I stood in line and I'll get mine."},{"time":1555000,"text":"I want an iPhone."},{"time":1559000,"text":"For what is a man?"},{"time":1561000,"text":"What has he got? If not iPhone,"},{"time":1564000,"text":"then he's got squat."},{"time":1567000,"text":"It's all the things a phone should be."},{"time":1570000,"text":"Who cares if it's AT&amp;T?"},{"time":1574000,"text":"I took a stand, paid half a grand!"},{"time":1580000,"text":"And I got an iPhone!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1587000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1590000,"text":"Thank you. Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1592000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}